Yehi ho moment jasko lagi pura region wait gardai thiyo‚Äîwho will rise as the PMSL CSA Fall Champion of 2025? üèÜ

Today, the SMASH RULE takes over:

üß® What is the SMASH RULE?

1Ô∏è‚É£ At the end of Day 2, the overall leader‚Äôs total points +10 will become the Match Point threshold.
2Ô∏è‚É£ Today is the day! Once a team reaches or exceeds the Match Point threshold, they must win a Chicken Dinner in a subsequent match to be crowned champions
3Ô∏è‚É£ Be the Champions! ‚Äì If no team meets both conditions by the end of all 18 matches, the team with the highest total points will be declared the champion.

Everything is on the line ‚ÄîTrophy, legacy, and one final zone.

snippet.title: Baahubali: The Epic - Official Trailer #2 (2025)
snippet.description:
Watch the new Baahubali: The Epic trailer for this upcoming film starring Prabhas, Rana Daggubati, Anushka Shetty, Tamannaah Bhatia, Sathyaraj, Ramya Krishnan, and Nassar.

Sivudu is an orphan who is rescued from a river as a baby and raised in a quiet tribal village at the foot of a towering waterfall. His world remains limited until a mysterious warrior‚Äôs mask falls from above, awakening a deep curiosity. Determined to discover its origin, he climbs the waterfall and uncovers a kingdom caught in the grip of tyranny and rebellion.

There he meets Avantika, a rebel fighting to rescue Devasena, a princess who has been wrongfully imprisoned for twenty-five years. Inspired by Avantika‚Äôs courage and driven by love, Sivudu joins the mission. When he enters Mahishmati and frees Devasena, the people begin to recognise him. During a confrontation, the royal guard Kattappa stops the fight and kneels before Sivudu, revealing that he is Mahendra Baahubali, the son of the noble prince Amarendra Baahubali.

The past unravels: Amarendra and his cousin Bhallaladeva were raised as heirs by the matriarch Sivagami. Though Amarendra was crowned king for his wisdom and compassion, Bhallaladeva‚Äôs jealousy led to betrayal. Manipulated by lies, Sivagami ordered Amarendra‚Äôs death, carried out by a loyal but misled Kattappa.

Now, Mahendra must rise. With Kattappa and the rebels beside him, he challenges Bhallaladeva, rescues Devasena, and reclaims the throne of Mahishmati.

10 years before RRR took the world by storm, master filmmaker S.S. Rajamouli redefined Indian Cinema with his two-part BAAHUBALI saga. Now, the epic tale of royalty, revenge, kings, and wars has been personally re-edited by the master himself from two films into a single unforgettable cinematic experience, with fully remastered picture and sound (and a few new surprises), so audiences can reunite to experience the euphoria the way it was intended: on the big screen.

Baahubali: The Epic, directed and written by SS Rajamouli, opens in theaters worldwide on October 31, 2025.

Atlee x Ranveer Singh team up with Sreeleela & Bobby Deol for the wildest cinematic explosion of action, drama, comedy & masala.

Yehi ho moment jasko lagi pura region wait gardai thiyo‚Äîwho will rise as the PMSL CSA Fall Champion of 2025? üèÜ

Today, the SMASH RULE takes over:

üß® What is the SMASH RULE?

1Ô∏è‚É£ At the end of Day 2, the overall leader‚Äôs total points +10 will become the Match Point threshold.
2Ô∏è‚É£ Today is the day! Once a team reaches or exceeds the Match Point threshold, they must win a Chicken Dinner in a subsequent match to be crowned champions
3Ô∏è‚É£ Be the Champions! ‚Äì If no team meets both conditions by the end of all 18 matches, the team with the highest total points will be declared the champion.

Chote

snippet.title: Arijit Singh - Aaj Se Teri | Akshay Kumar & Radhika Apte | Amit Trivedi | Padman | Lyrical
snippet.description:
Song - Aaj Se Teri
Singer - Arijit Singh
Music - Amit Trivedi
Lyricist - Kausar Munir

Lyrics:
Mukhda -
Aaj Se Teri Saari Galiyaan Meri Ho Gayi, 
Aaj Se Mera Ghar Tera Ho Gaya‚Ä¶

Aaj Se Teri Saari Galiyaan Meri Ho Gayi, 
Aaj Se Mera Ghar Tera Ho Gaya‚Ä¶
Aaj Se Meri Saari Khushiyaan Teri Ho Gayi,
Aaj Se Tera Gum Mera Ho Gaya. 

Ho Tere Kandhe Ka Jo Til Hai, 
Ho Tera Seene Mein Jo Dil Hai, 
Ho Teri Bijli Ka Jo Bill Hai-
Aaj Se Mera Ho Gaya‚Ä¶

Ho Mere Khwabon Ka Ambar,
Ho Meri Khushiyon Ka Samandar,
Ho Mere Pin Code Ka Number-
Aaj Se Tera Ho Gaya. 

Antara 1- 
Tere Maathe Aaaaa‚Ä¶.Tere Maathe Ke Kumkum Ko
Main Tilak Lagaa Ke Ghoomoonga, 
Teri Baali Ki Chhunchhun Ko
Main Dil Se Lagaa Ke Jhoomoonga‚Ä¶

Meri Chhoti Si Bhoolon, 
Ko Tu Nadiya Mein Baha Dena.
Tere Jude Ke Phoolon Ko, 
Main Apne Shirt Mein Pehnoonga.

Bas Mere Liye Tu Maalpue Kabhi Kabhi Bana Dena‚Ä¶

Aaj Se Meri Saari Ratiyaan Teri Ho Gayi, 
Aaj Se Tera Din Mera Ho Gaya. 

Ho Tere Kandhe Ka Jo Til Hai, 
Ho Tera Seene Mein Jo Dil Hai, 
Ho Teri Bijli Ka Jo Bill Hai-
Aaj Se Mera Ho Gaya‚Ä¶

Ho Mere Khwabon Ka Ambar,
Ho Meri Khushiyon Ka Samandar,
Ho Mere Pin Code Ka Number-
Aaj Se Tera Ho Gaya. 

Antara 2-
Tu Maange Sardi Mein Amiya, 
Jo Maange Garmi Mein Mungphaliyaan, 
Tu Baarish Mein Agar Keh De,
Ja Mere Liye Tu Dhoop Khila.

Toh Main Sooraj‚Ä¶‚Ä¶. Toh Main Sooraj Ko Jhatak Doonga, 
Toh Main Saawan Ko Gatak Loonga,
Toh Saare Taaron Sang Chanda
Main Teri Goad Mein Rakh Doonga-

Bas Mere Liye Tu Khil Ke Kabhi Muskuraa Dena‚Ä¶

Aaj Se Meri Saari Sadiyaan Teri Ho Gayi, 
Aaj Se Tera Pal Mera Ho Gaya. 

Ho Tere Kandhe Ka Jo Til Hai, 
Ho Tere Seene Mein Jo Dil Hai, 
Ho Teri Bijli Ka Jo Bill Hai-
Aaj Se Mera Ho Gaya‚Ä¶

Ho Mere Khwaabon Ka Ambar,
Ho Meri Khushiyon Ka Samandar,
Ho Mere Pin Code Ka Number-
Aaj Se ‚Ä¶‚Ä¶Tera Ho Gaya.

The Gayatri Mantra is a powerful and ancient chant from Hinduism. It is believed to bring peace, prosperity, and spiritual guidance for those who recite it. The mantra is a prayer to the divine light and wisdom that illuminates our path towards enlightenment. It is traditionally chanted before and after meditation, and is often used during yoga practices. The Gayatri Mantra is considered to be one of the most sacred of all mantras, and is said to have the power to protect and purify the mind, body, and soul.

The Gayatri Mantra is a powerful and ancient chant from Hinduism. It is believed to bring peace, prosperity, and spiritual guidance for those who recite it. The mantra is a prayer to the divine light and wisdom that illuminates our path towards enlightenment. It is traditionally chanted before and after meditation, and is often used during yoga practices. The Gayatri Mantra is considered to be one of the most sacred of all mantras, and is said to have the power to protect and purify the mind, body, and soul.

snippet.title: Kuber Ashtalakshmi Dhanprapti Mantra With Lyrics | Kubera Lakshmi Mantra | Dhanteras | Diwali
snippet.description:
Kuber Ashtalakshmi Dhanprapti Mantra With Lyrics | Kubera Lakshmi Mantra | Dhanteras | Diwali 

Welcome to this divine chant ‚Äî Kuber Ashtalakshmi Mantra With Lyrics, a sacred and powerful Diwali Mantra for attracting wealth, prosperity, and abundance. Chanting the Kuber Mantra 108 Times invokes the combined blessings of Lord Kuber, the treasurer of the gods, and Ashta Lakshmi, the eight forms of Mahalakshmi ‚Äî the goddess of wealth, fortune, and divine prosperity.

ü™î Kuber Ashtalakshmi Mantra is one of the most auspicious Bhakti Songs to chant during Diwali, Dhanteras, and Friday Lakshmi Puja. This sacred vibration opens the doors to financial growth, success, and inner peace.

‚ú® Kuber Ashtalakshmi Mantra With Lyrics brings harmony between spiritual wealth and material prosperity. Lord Kuber blesses with the resources to sustain your goals, while Ashta Lakshmi ensures divine flow of fortune and blessings.

üé∂ Repeat these divine names with full devotion while listening to Kuber Ashtalakshmi Mantra With Lyrics, and experience the transformation in your energy and fortune.

üî• Why Chant This Mantra:

Brings prosperity and financial stability

Attracts positive vibrations and abundance energy

Removes karmic blockages related to wealth

Ideal for Diwali, Friday Puja, and Kuber Puja

üí∞ When chanted during Diwali nights, this Kuber Ashtalakshmi Mantra opens up the spiritual channel for divine fortune. Chant along with lyrics to immerse yourself in divine vibrations and experience the blessings of Lord Kuber and Mahalakshmi in your life.

üéµ Listen, meditate, and let this Kuber Mantra 108 Times bring peace, prosperity, and spiritual growth. Share this Kuber Ashtalakshmi Mantra With Lyrics with your family and friends this Diwali and spread the blessings of Lakshmi Kuber across all homes.

Title :- Kuber Ashtalakshmi Stotra

snippet.title: Bipul Chettri - Ghar Salkay ko Katha
snippet.description:
The second release from the upcoming album 'Pravah', was composed by Bipul‚Äôs father, Late Nirendra Mohan Chettri and written by the Late Shri Laxman Shrimal, a Sahitya Akademi awardee, poet, author and a celebrated playwright in the Nepali language, both of whom were contemporaries from Kurseong, Darjeeling. Rearranged beautifully by Bipul and Pranai Gurung, the song has been brought back to life in a style that is in the mood of a laid back soul/jazz feel, which very rarely makes it into the Nepali music styles nowadays but was occasionally used in the '70s, when this song was written and composed.

Please Press 'CC' to read subtitles in English and Nepali lyrics.

MUSIC
Bipul Chettri - Vocals  
Pranai Gurung - Guitars
Rahul Rai - Bass
Rythem Bansal - Piano
Shantanu Sudarshan - Drums

Lyrics by Late Laxman Shrimal & Composition by Late Nirendra Mohan Chettri
Re-arranged by Bipul Chettri & Pranai Gurung
Recording Engineers - Jonty Indra, Anindo Bose, Ritwik De 
Mixed & Mastered by Binaya Man Amatya
Producer - Bipul Chettri
Executive Producer - Sonam Tashi 

MUSIC VIDEO
Director of Photography: Vashistha Pradhan
Editors: Tejistha Pradhan & VAZZU
Colorist: Shiny Syco
Stylist: Pfulmaya
Hair and Make up: Reena Tomar
Production House: Lasta Stuido
Production: Rahul Rai
Line Production & Location Manager: Adrian Pradhan 
Gaffer: Krishan Dev Bharti
Camera in-charge: Govind Kumar
Camera Attendant: Rahul Acharya
Light Assistance: Qutubuddin
Light Boys: Mahesh Kumar Ram, Arvind Kumar, Vikram Singh 
Location Team: Amit Kumar, Qutubuddin, Ramesh Kumar 
Location: OddBird Theatre, New Delhi.

All Rights Reserved by Bipul Chettri, except wherein mentioned. 2025.

Hai tere pyar mein jab se

Mai√± qaid hu√±

snippet.description:
You‚Äôve seen them dance, you‚Äôve seen them fall in love, now witness the heartbreak when love gets intertwined! Presenting ‚ÄòTumse Behtar‚Äô from ‚ÄòSunny Sanskari Ki Tulsi Kumari‚Äô, starring Varun Dhawan, Janhvi Kapoor, Sanya Malhotra and Rohit Saraf. Composed by Tanishk Bagchi and written by Manoj Muntashir, this beautiful song is sung by Arijit Singh.

#TumseBehtar #ArijitSingh #TanishkBagchi #SSKTK

Music Composer: Tanishk Bagchi
Lyricist: Manoj Muntashir
Singer: Arijit Singh
Music Producer: Tanishk Bagchi & Krishna Kishor
Woodwinds: Nikhil Ram
Keys: Navneeth, Anoop, Melvin
Male Chorus: Rahul, Sanjay, Abijith, Aston
Female Chorus: Kamalaja, Fathima, Nayansi, Aarthi
Arijit Singh's Vocals Recorded by: Sukanto Singha
Arijit Singh‚Äôs Recordings Managed by: Ashish Biswal
Mixed and Mastered by: Eric Pillai @ Future Sounds of Bombay
Assistant Mix Engineer: Michael Edwin Pillai @ Future Sounds of Bombay
Music Supervisor: Azeem Dayani and Varun Dhawan
Sr Associate Music Supervisor: Tanvi Asher
Jr Associate Music Supervisor: Vasundhara Misra
Music Team: Heer Kamdar

Dharma Productions & Mentor Disciple Entertainment present 
A Dharma Productions Film
Starring Varun Dhawan, Janhvi Kapoor, Sanya Malhotra, & Rohit Saraf
Directed by Shashank Khaitan
Produced by Hiroo Yash Johar, Karan Johar, Adar Poonawalla, Apoorva Mehta & Shashank Khaitan
Co-produced by Marijke deSouza 
Written by Shashank Khaitan
Dialogues by Shashank Khaitan & Ishita Moitra
